## 📁 File Structure

| Sheet Name        | Description                                       |
|-------------------|---------------------------------------------------|
| `Sales Data`      | Cleaned version of raw sales data                 |
| `Pivot Report`    | Pivot Table-based dashboard and analysis summary  |

